+ BROADCASTPLAYER +
Broadcasts a message to specific player(s).
Action type: Broadcast
Usage: BROADCASTPLAYER <PLAYERS> <DURATION> <MESSAGE>


Arguments:
<players>
  Required: YES
  Type: Player List
  The players to show. Variables are supported.

<duration>
  Required: YES
  Type: Float (Number)
  The duration of the message. Variables are supported.

<message>
  Required: YES
  Type: String (Message/Text)
  The message. Variables are supported.
